uctures are eventually discussed,\nin the context of clarifying the conditions for water transport at low\ntemperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 May 2013 14:11:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2013 11:21:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2013 09:20:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-18"}
